title: Tales of Plymothia
description:
TALES OF PLYMOTHIA



The acclaimed game from Indie Developer Hanzoid Prod
Now avalible for PC.

Cast overbord in a storm youre saved by an unknown girl. 
You have no idea what lies ahead of you.

Slowly you unravel a fate which will turn you into
someone new.
Sometimes the past is best left behind.





 
JRPG 

Best played with xbox 360 controller.

System Requirements:

Processor: AMD Athlon 900+, Pentium 800

Graphic card: Radeon 9800xt or equivalent (Direct x 8)

Ram: 512mb


Please comment below and give the thumbs up if you feel so enclined

Thank you for playing the game it means the world to us





INSTALL NOTES:

Just unpack the folder at desired location and play.
